{"tid":2258123,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟放低適合幼貓嘅乾糧/罐罐！","createTime":"2020-10-25T18:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T06:10:48.000Z","uid":378659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aae8ba199a9250153d62c84fa8a38f720361b543","tid":2258123,"uid":378659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:33:46.000Z","msg":"6個月大 美短 <br />\n而家食緊wellness core嘅幼貓糧！<br />\n罐頭就食緊Thrive!!<br />\n都食咗有一排<br />\n想幫佢轉下其他糧食<br />\n大家有冇咩好介紹😋<br />\n附送一下主子照片一張😚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQ58vdY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQ58vdY.jpg&h=0dbb0c92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSXfadZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSXfadZ.png&h=16fafb46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1298f74bd8da4188fd8ebce52302c8d8355bf910","tid":2258123,"uid":322746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:54:49.000Z","msg":"轉乾濕糧冇咩大分別<br />\n一係直接食生肉<br />\n一係間唔中食下生雞頸 雞翼 當洗牙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6drfUNO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6drfUNO.jpg&h=01200dda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efd3a59d08183ba3f268a8e1851208a2139f568f","tid":2258123,"uid":345286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T19:44:30.000Z","msg":"如果餵流浪貓最好餵咩"},{"pid":"53c2b840d2eee815b4e9925254745baec6e1b313","tid":2258123,"uid":243306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T23:57:59.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n但食緊wellness core 紫色包裝個隻幼貓糧"},{"pid":"9050fc8b78786820ce4a07a6fd96b1de4ae247a1","tid":2258123,"uid":39703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T01:32:51.000Z","msg":"Nulo糧有埋益生菌"},{"pid":"484ff7b52721daa524139277ae003a20e5706544","tid":2258123,"uid":55081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:49:56.000Z","msg":"我家主子三個零月大，之前屙軟便一直食hills 腸胃處方糧同罐。好返食緊applaws 幼貓乾糧 (買唔到wellness core)，濕糧轉咗thrive 幼